## 1. Global Visual System

### 1.1 Color palette (high-impact, civic)

Use a bolder, darker base so the content feels serious and newsy.

**Core**

* `bg.page`: `#050816` (very dark blue-black body background)
* `bg.page-alt`: `#0B1220` (alternate dark for some bands)
* `bg.card`: `#FFFFFF`
* `accent.orange`: `#F97316` (main highlight / CTAs / â€œimpactâ€)
* `accent.teal`: `#14B8A6` (wins / positive stories)
* `accent.blue`: `#0EA5E9` (links, data highlights)

**Status**

* `status.answered`: `#16A34A`
* `status.pending`: `#FACC15`
* `status.overdue`: `#EF4444`
* `status.appeal`: `#6366F1`

**Text**

* `text.on-dark`: `#E5E7EB`
* `text.primary`: `#020617`
* `text.secondary`: `#4B5563`
* `text.muted`: `#9CA3AF`

**Neutrals**

* `border.subtle`: `#E5E7EB`
* `bg.row-alt`: `#F3F4F6`

### 1.2 Typography

* Display / headlines: **DM Serif Display** (or similar), used only for H1/H2.
* Body & UI: **Inter / system-ui**.

Scale (desktop):

* `H1`: 40px / 1.1, serif, 600
* `H2`: 28px, serif, 600
* `H3`: 18px, sans, 600
* `Body`: 15â€“16px, sans, 400
* `Label/Meta`: 12â€“13px, 500, uppercase, letterspacing +0.06em

### 1.3 Layout & cards

* Max width: 1200â€“1240px, centered.
* 12-column grid, 24px gutters.
* Page padding: 24px (desktop), 16px (mobile).
* Section vertical spacing: 48px between major sections.
* Card style (default):

  * Background: `#FFFFFF`
  * Radius: 16px
  * Border: `1px solid #E5E7EB`
  * Shadow: `0 12px 30px rgba(15,23,42,0.16)`
  * Padding: 20â€“24px

### 1.4 Iconography (no photos)

* Use a single stroke icon set (e.g. Tabler/Heroicons-style):

  * 20â€“24px, 1.75px stroke, rounded caps.
* For topics, use **colored icon tiles**:

  * Square `32px` with 8px radius, filled with topic color and white icon inside.
  * Ex: Health `#DC2626`, Education `#3B82F6`, Infrastructure `#4B5563`, Environment `#059669`.

